snippet.title: 10 More Bullets - iOS / Android - HD Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
10 More Bullets by Michel Gérard (iOS / Android)

So, how many ships can you destroy with 10 more bullets ?

In this sequel of "10 Bullets", the objective remains the same : wait for the perfect spot and shoot to trigger massive chain reaction.

And this time, upgrading your hero and collecting in game boosters will make it a total destruction.

iTunes Store Page:

https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id867525916

Google Play:

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gringogames.tenmorebullets

Homepage:

http://www.gringogames.com/
